    "body": "@davidkna the `en_US.UTF-8` is the only locale I have in my system:\n\n```\n...\n#en_IL UTF-8\n#en_IN UTF-8\n#en_NG UTF-8\n#en_NZ.UTF-8 UTF-8\n#en_NZ ISO-8859-1\n#en_PH.UTF-8 UTF-8\n#en_PH ISO-8859-1\n#en_SC.UTF-8 UTF-8\n#en_SG.UTF-8 UTF-8\n#en_SG ISO-8859-1\nen_US.UTF-8 UTF-8\n#en_US ISO-8859-1\n#en_ZA.UTF-8 UTF-8\n#en_ZA ISO-8859-1\n#en_ZM UTF-8\n#en_ZW.UTF-8 UTF-8\n#en_ZW ISO-8859-1\n#eo UTF-8\n...\n```",
